      &lt;img alt="A John Deere Tractor driving in a field." src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/QilzyFe4zezXM4DL9xIdRtdlZ_k=/0x0:3000x2000/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73342579/john_deere_4.0.jpg" /&gt;
