      &lt;img alt="A screenshot of the loading screen from Abe’s Oddysee." src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/K-9cbQlRrFpjLahQPueyx9ik99A=/394x0:2163x1179/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73342369/IMG_4573.0.png" /&gt;
